            "id": "11",
            "title": "Nominate for the Q1 2024 Technology Game Changer Awards!",
            "publishedDate": "2024-05-07",
            "modalContent": {
              "Text": "<h2>A Message from the People Team</h2><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">Hi team,</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">Nominations for the next round of&nbsp;<strong>Technology Game Changers awards ARE OPEN TODAY</strong>! As a reminder, these awards are designed to recognize full-time colleagues across Technology who have done exceptional work that’s made a significant impact on our OKRs and embody Condé Nast’s values. The winners selected for this round will be&nbsp;<strong>based on their performance and impact in Q1 2024.</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>Details</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">We will recognize:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">Six full-time individuals across Technology via colleague nominations (monetary)</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">Three Technology teams via LT nomination (non-monetary)</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">Two individuals based on Condé Celebrates</span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>How it Works</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>Individual Awards</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>Nominations:</strong> All employees in Technology can nominate any fellow full-time colleague for an award — in any market, team, or title. You must describe and provide results for their game-changing work in helping Technology meet its OKRs and choose which CN value your nominee exemplified most.&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://forms.gle/yDyx3S97ShZUAkzL9\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong><u>All nominations must go through this Google form</u></strong></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><u>.</u></span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>Winner Selection:&nbsp;</strong>Winners will be selected by a cross-functional panel made up of a diverse group of Technology and People team members.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>Award Announcement:&nbsp;</strong>Winners will be announced at the next Town Hall and win 250 USD.</span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>Team Awards</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>Winner Selection:</strong> The Technology Leadership team meets to decide which three cross-functional teams will be recognized.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>Award Announcement</strong>: Winning teams will be recognized at the next Town Hall and receive swag items. There is no monetary reward for this spotlight.</span></li><li>&nbsp;</li></ul><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>Condé Celebrates Awards</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>Winner selection:&nbsp;</strong>The individual who received the most e-cards and the individual who sent the most e-cards in Q1 ‘24 (data-driven).</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>Award Announcement:&nbsp;</strong>Winners will be announced at the next Town Hall and each receive game-changer swag!</span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong>What We Ask of You</strong></span></p><p><a href=\"https://forms.gle/yDyx3S97ShZUAkzL9\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Nominate your colleagues using this google form by May 22</u></strong></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">&nbsp; and recognize your colleagues on&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://condenast.rewardgateway.com/SmartHub\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><u>Condé Celebrates</u></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">. The winners will be announced at our next Town Hall in June.&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">We can’t wait to celebrate our winners! If you have any questions, please contact&nbsp;</span><a href=\"mailto:bridget.glynn-baker@condenast.com\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><u>Bridget Gynn-Baker</u></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"> or&nbsp;</span><a href=\"mailto:Shrusthi_Umarji@condenast.com\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\"><u>Shrusthi Umarji</u></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">Thanks,</span></p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:'Libre Franklin',sans-serif;\">The People Team</span></p>",
              "modalTitle": null
            }
