              "Text": "<h2>A Message from: The Technology Leadership Team</h2><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\">Hi all,</span></p><p><br><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\">Thanks to those who attended last week's Technology Town Hall. If you weren't able to make it, please&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://technology.condenast.com/contentpresentationlibrary?tab=townhallrecordings\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\"><strong><u>view the recording here</u></strong></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\">.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\">We'd like your feedback!&nbsp;Please<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span><a href=\"https://forms.gle/fF6vGZtpHAcd8fpMA\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\"><strong><u>complete this short survey</u></strong></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\">&nbsp;to tell us what you liked and how we can improve future sessions.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\"><strong>Congrats to our Game Changer Winners!</strong></span><br>&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://technology.condenast.com/eventcalender\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;\"><u>Read more about why these individuals went above and beyond in Q4 2023</u></span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;\">!</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\"><strong>Daniel Jacobsberg</strong>,&nbsp;Software Engineer, UK</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\"><strong>Chris Landaeta</strong>, Lead, Designer, Spain</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\"><strong>Suneeth Lenin</strong>, Software Engineer III, India</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\"><strong>Anna Pagan</strong>, Sr. Product Manager, UK</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\"><strong>Rashmi Rao</strong>,&nbsp;Software Engineer III, India</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\"><strong>Manthan Raut</strong>, Software Engineer I, India</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\"><strong>Karthik RP</strong>, Senior Developer, India</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\"><strong>Shaik Tasneem Saleem</strong>, BI Engineer I, India</span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;\"><strong>Team Winners</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\">Vogue Runway PoC &amp; Mastadon</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\">Image Search and Bounce Modelling (Data Science)</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\">Content Applications</span><br>&nbsp;</li></ul><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;\"><strong>Condé Celebrates Winners</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\">Francis Devinney (received most recognition)</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,100%);\">Manthan Raut (sent most recognition)</span><br>&nbsp;</li></ul>",
